Aku bisa kok.

249
00:16:15,190 --> 00:16:16,560
Mau susu hangat?

250
00:16:17,020 --> 00:16:17,880
Aku bikinin ya, tunggu.

251
00:16:32,270 --> 00:16:33,790
Susu plus madu.

252
00:16:34,420 --> 00:16:36,160
Katanya, minum susu plus madu sebelum tidur

253
00:16:36,160 --> 00:16:37,400
bisa bantu biar tidur lebih nyenyak.

254
00:16:48,860 --> 00:16:50,840
Apa pun kamu bikin pasti manis banget ya?

255
00:16:51,250 --> 00:16:52,610
Hah?

256
00:16:52,820 --> 00:16:54,200
Aku...

257
00:16:56,220 --> 00:16:57,970
Kok kamu tahu sih?

258
00:17:01,290 --> 00:17:04,080
Kalau nggak ada apa-apa, aku tidur dulu.

259
00:17:05,360 --> 00:17:05,960
Selamat malam.

260
00:17:12,890 --> 00:17:14,920
Kamu mau bawa aku ke mana? Hei, tunggu!

261
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:20,110
Tidur di sini aja.

262
00:17:20,820 --> 00:17:23,720
Nggak apa-apa, aku bisa tidur di luar.

263
00:17:23,840 --> 00:17:25,520
Di luar kamu berisik banget.

264
00:17:25,660 --> 00:17:26,980
Aku nggak bisa tidur.

265
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:09,520
Bangun!

266
00:19:11,890 --> 00:19:13,330
Sudah pagi.

267
00:19:13,350 --> 00:19:15,730
Sudah hampir jam tujuh, aku telat nih!

268
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:18,260
Jam tujuh pagi?

269
00:19:18,460 --> 00:19:20,100
Kenapa pagi-pagi udah bangun?

270
00:19:20,850 --> 00:19:22,580
Ayo ganti baju, buruan!

271
00:19:22,690 --> 00:19:25,170
Aku siang baru ada kelas.

272
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:27,870
Aku tunggu di luar, jangan lama-lama.

273
00:19:34,460 --> 00:19:35,800
Ngantuk banget, aku.

274
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:47,600
Mau pakai punyaku dulu nggak?

275
00:19:47,600 --> 00:19:49,160
Oh, makasih.

276
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:50,760
Udah siap, langsung pergi.

277
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:54,200
Ngapain buru-buru?

278
00:20:07,660 --> 00:20:09,950
- Kenapa naik ini sih? - Aku lagi buru-buru.

279
00:20:09,970 --> 00:20:11,360
Pegang ini.

280
00:20:14,420 --> 00:20:15,720
Kenapa lambat amat?

281
00:20:26,650 --> 00:20:28,060
Naik.

282
00:20:40,430 --> 00:20:41,990
Pegangan, ya.

283
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:14,190
Takut banget ya?

284
00:21:14,270 --> 00:21:16,390
Lihat deh cara kamu nyetir.

285
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:19,800
- OK, aku mau kuliah. - Hei!

286
00:21:20,170 --> 00:21:21,710
Terus aku gimana?

287
00:21:22,010 --> 00:21:23,580
Aku kelasnya siang.

288
00:21:24,080 --> 00:21:26,150
Mau ikut kuliah bareng aku?

289
00:21:26,350 --> 00:21:28,450
Ngapain ikut kamu? Enggak ah.

290
00:21:28,460 --> 00:21:30,150
Aku telepon temanku aja, suruh jemput.

291
00:21:30,340 --> 00:21:32,090
Oke, aku pergi dulu ya.

292
00:21:53,860 --> 00:21:55,240
(P', uangmu ketinggalan di jaket.)

293
00:21:55,730 --> 00:21:57,200
(Pakai aja.)

294
00:22:01,300 --> 00:22:02,870
(Kenapa aku perlu simpan?)

295
00:22:03,840 --> 00:22:05,650
(Kan dompetmu ketinggalan?)

296
00:22:08,410 --> 00:22:11,430
(Serius nih buat aku? Jangan tambah utangku ya.)

297
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:50,000
North.

298
00:22:50,390 --> 00:22:54,480
Malam belum puas, pagi dibangunin lagi.

299
00:22:55,410 --> 00:22:57,860
Aku nggak tahu mau hubungi siapa lagi.

300
00:22:58,190 --> 00:23:00,360
Kenapa?

301
00:23:00,460 --> 00:23:01,550
Bro.

302
00:23:01,670 --> 00:23:03,550
Bisa bantu aku nggak?

303
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:06,470
Apa?

304
00:23:07,330 --> 00:23:08,990
Jemput aku.

305
00:23:09,890 --> 00:23:11,800
P'Johan ninggalin aku di kampus.

306
00:23:12,530 --> 00:23:14,080
Aku kelasnya siang.

307
00:23:17,460 --> 00:23:18,850
Tunggu.

308
00:23:23,340 --> 00:23:24,950
Sialan.

309
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:29,320
Sial beneran.

310
00:23:30,260 --> 00:23:32,760
Ngapain sih, Nao? Sakit tau!

311
00:23:33,570 --> 00:23:36,040
- Aku balik. - Ada apa?

312
00:23:36,130 --> 00:23:39,220
Suer ngomong sendiri, terus meluk aku.

313
00:23:39,250 --> 00:23:41,150
Pantes semalam nggak nyaman.

314
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:43,360
Udah aku tendang dari kasur kok.

315
00:23:43,940 --> 00:23:45,360
Santai aja.

316
00:23:45,820 --> 00:23:46,480
Naik.

317
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:49,360
Jam berapa kuliah?

318
00:23:54,830 --> 00:23:56,880
Jam sembilan pagi, kenapa?

319
00:23:57,060 --> 00:23:59,300
Kamu bisa jemput North di Fakultas Kedokteran?

320
00:24:00,540 --> 00:24:02,500
Kenapa harus aku?

321
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:04,810
Dengar nggak?

322
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:08,360
Katanya: "Kenapa harus aku?"

323
00:24:09,530 --> 00:24:13,130
Tanya dong, "Kamu yakin ngomong gitu?"

324
00:24:13,800 --> 00:24:15,740
"Atau aku yang bilang aja?"

325
00:24:16,970 --> 00:24:18,120
Kata dia,

326
00:24:18,570 --> 00:24:21,270
"Kamu yakin ngomong gitu?"

327
00:24:21,300 --> 00:24:24,150
"Atau aku bilang aja?" Bilang apa?

328
00:24:24,490 --> 00:24:26,500
Kalian ngomongin apa sih?

329
00:24:26,570 --> 00:24:28,100
Aku aja yang ngomong sama dia.

330
00:24:29,930 --> 00:24:30,980
Ada apa sih kalian?

331
00:24:31,810 --> 00:24:32,720
North.

332
00:24:34,960 --> 00:24:37,170
Kamu nggak jago bohong deh.

333
00:24:38,600 --> 00:24:41,810
Biasanya aku jago, gara-gara telponmu jadi kacau.

334
00:24:41,820 --> 00:24:44,910
Harimau kecil yang kasihan.

335
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:47,840
Jangan lupa teh hijaunya!

336
00:24:47,860 --> 00:24:50,280
Siap, aku beliin, Pak!

337
00:24:50,390 --> 00:24:52,290
Aku jemput ya.

338
00:24:53,700 --> 00:24:54,930
Ini buat kamu.

339
00:25:28,520 --> 00:25:30,040
Naik mobil, bodoh.

340
00:25:31,650 --> 00:25:32,840
Kamu juga pakai.

341
00:25:34,140 --> 00:25:36,590
Ngapain lihat-lihat lagi? Ayo naik.

342
00:25:45,020 --> 00:25:46,310
Ayo pergi.

343
00:26:14,290 --> 00:26:18,560
Gimana rasanya pagi-pagi ditendang keluar kasur?

344
00:26:19,670 --> 00:26:20,560
Rasanya kayak

345
00:26:21,670 --> 00:26:23,150
ditendang sama kucing.

346
00:26:24,950 --> 00:26:26,150
Ya ampun.

347
00:26:26,610 --> 00:26:29,360
Kapten tim bola, Raja Pesta Teknik.

348
00:26:29,370 --> 00:26:30,340
Gila kamu.

349
00:26:30,350 --> 00:26:31,900
Pertanyaannya kok bikin aku sedih sih.

350
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:34,630
- Karena kamu lah! - Siapa sangka...

351
00:26:34,650 --> 00:26:39,970
Kamu kok bisa sekasian itu, ngomong sendiri, terus meluk dia.

352
00:26:40,890 --> 00:26:42,920
Tunggu aja, jangan kasih aku bahan.

353
00:26:43,020 --> 00:26:46,320
Giliranku dong nanti, bro. Sana!

354
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:48,990
Belikan aku teh hijau sana!

355
00:26:49,000 --> 00:26:51,700
- Mau teh hijau. - Siap, bos.

356
00:26:55,400 --> 00:26:57,390
(North, kamu ngapain ke Johan?)

357
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:01,320
(Ada apa?)

358
00:27:02,440 --> 00:27:04,150
(Johan nambahin tiga utang lagi di akunmu.)

359
00:27:05,390 --> 00:27:06,330
Hah?

360
00:27:07,750 --> 00:27:08,970
(Tiga kali.)

361
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:13,470
(Iya, makanya aku tanya. Kalau mau transfer bilang aja.)

362
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:17,550
Aku ngapain sih, sampai utangnya nambah?

363
00:27:22,170 --> 00:27:23,790
(Kenapa kamu gituin aku?)

364
00:27:27,570 --> 00:27:28,500
Nih.

365
00:27:32,260 --> 00:27:33,310
Makasih.

366
00:27:33,630 --> 00:27:35,130
Taruh aja di sana.

367
00:27:35,190 --> 00:27:35,760
Aku mau kuliah dulu.

368
00:27:35,760 --> 00:27:38,100
Pergi aja, aku baru kelas siang.

369
00:27:38,600 --> 00:27:39,790
- Siang. - Iya.

370
00:27:39,810 --> 00:27:41,790
Mau ke mana? Mau bareng?

371
00:27:41,820 --> 00:27:45,370
Nggak usah, kamu aja. Aku nggak apa-apa, jangan khawatir.

372
00:27:46,090 --> 00:27:48,030
Kamu pikir aku peduli sama kamu?

373
00:27:49,990 --> 00:27:51,230
Cepat sana pergi.

374
00:27:53,520 --> 00:27:54,540
Ger.

375
00:27:54,830 --> 00:27:56,220
Makasih.

376
00:28:07,350 --> 00:28:09,080
(Beneran di-read doang nih?)

377
00:28:09,610 --> 00:28:11,270
(Tentang utang tambahan itu)

378
00:28:11,780 --> 00:28:14,510
(Kamu kasih uang, tapi nambahin utang aku?)

379
00:28:23,030 --> 00:28:24,060
Jo

380
00:28:24,390 --> 00:28:28,110
Kamu nggak ngopi di fakultas teknik hari ini?

381
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:33,110
Lihat ekspresimu, pagi ini pasti sudah
ketemu adikmu, ya.

382
00:28:35,620 --> 00:28:36,570
Ton

383
00:28:37,290 --> 00:28:39,390
Temanmu mau pensiun dari dunia lamanya.

384
00:28:39,760 --> 00:28:42,670
Tapi dia benar-benar bungkam,
nggak seperti biasanya.

385
00:28:44,380 --> 00:28:47,050
Pantas saja dia sangat tertutup.

386
00:28:47,200 --> 00:28:48,970
Tapi aku tetap nggak paham.

387
00:28:49,090 --> 00:28:50,900
Dia nggak pernah seperti ini ke orang lain.

388
00:28:51,350 --> 00:28:53,090
Kenapa yang satu ini berbeda?

389
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:55,090
Sejujurnya, ceritanya cukup panjang.

390
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:56,260
Semacam...

391
00:28:57,370 --> 00:29:01,340
Dia tipe idealnya Jo, gitu lho.

392
00:29:03,170 --> 00:29:04,530
Masa sih?

393
00:29:04,820 --> 00:29:06,100
Sampai lututnya lemas begitu.

394
00:29:06,130 --> 00:29:10,200
Ini bukan sekadar soal tipe, tahu.

395
00:29:10,390 --> 00:29:12,340
Hill, kamu kebanyakan ngomong deh.

396
00:29:12,350 --> 00:29:14,530
Jangan sampai aku ceritain kamu dan Ter!

397
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:18,050
Eh, cerita apa tuh?

398
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:22,600
Hei.

399
00:29:22,690 --> 00:29:26,520
Aku mau wawancara kamu, bisakah sekarang?

400
00:29:26,670 --> 00:29:27,930
Boleh.

401
00:29:28,510 --> 00:29:30,740
- Di sana, ya? - Oke.

402
00:29:32,080 --> 00:29:34,270
Lagi pada ngapain, nih?

403
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:36,290
- Nulis laporan. - Oh.

404
00:29:36,310 --> 00:29:38,470
Nggak cuma laporan aja, kok.

405
00:29:39,230 --> 00:29:41,550
Kayaknya ada yang lagi kangen
seseorang, deh.

406
00:29:43,300 --> 00:29:45,250
Siapa tuh orangnya?

407
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:49,900
Nggak bisa kasih tahu kami, ya?

408
00:29:51,370 --> 00:29:53,750
Mungkin nanti setelah aku berhasil,
aku akan bilang.

409
00:29:55,290 --> 00:29:58,240
Menurutmu, orang itu lagi nonton nggak?

410
00:30:01,420 --> 00:30:02,610
Sepertinya, iya.

411
00:30:02,630 --> 00:30:05,770
Mau bilang sesuatu untuk dia?

412
00:30:09,860 --> 00:30:11,020
Aku kangen kamu.

413
00:30:14,190 --> 00:30:16,770
Dia dari fakultas mana? Mau kasih bocoran?

414
00:30:17,470 --> 00:30:18,910
Mau tebak dulu nggak?

415
00:30:20,950 --> 00:30:23,650
Mahasiswa kedokteran? Atau dari keperawatan?

416
00:30:24,420 --> 00:30:25,460
Bukan.

417
00:30:25,590 --> 00:30:27,160
Manajemen?

418
00:30:28,130 --> 00:30:29,000
Bukan juga.

419
00:30:29,020 --> 00:30:31,140
Teknik?

420
00:30:31,940 --> 00:30:34,390
Salah. Aku kasih satu kesempatan lagi.

421
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:37,370
Udah deh, acak saja tebakannya.

422
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:39,180
Anak Fakultas Kedokteran Hewan.

423
00:30:42,760 --> 00:30:43,830
Bener!

424
00:30:44,460 --> 00:30:46,880
Akhirnya kita punya petunjuk!

425
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:48,800
Aku ada satu pertanyaan terakhir.

426
00:30:48,800 --> 00:30:50,830
Habis itu nggak ganggu lagi, deh.

427
00:30:50,870 --> 00:30:52,480
Kalau nanti kalian jadian beneran,

428
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:54,670
apa yang mau kamu ucapkan ke dia?

429
00:31:00,550 --> 00:31:02,150
Aku akan selalu menjaga kamu.

430
00:31:03,950 --> 00:31:05,770
Kenapa bukan aku orangnya?

431
00:31:05,780 --> 00:31:09,680
Terima kasih banyak. Makasih, ya!

432
00:31:10,370 --> 00:31:12,430
Makasih. Yuk, pergi.

433
00:31:13,780 --> 00:31:15,370
"Aku akan selalu menjaga kamu."

434
00:31:16,800 --> 00:31:19,740
- "Aku akan selalu menjaga kamu."
- Pasti nada kayak gitu, deh.

435
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:39,770
Ter

436
00:31:41,910 --> 00:31:43,240
Hai, P'Thunmild.

437
00:31:44,630 --> 00:31:45,980
Lagi mau beli minuman ya?

438
00:31:46,520 --> 00:31:47,420
Iya.

439
00:31:50,690 --> 00:31:52,920
Boleh ngobrol bentar?

440
00:31:58,010 --> 00:31:58,970
Tentu saja.

441
00:32:03,910 --> 00:32:05,310
Apa kabar?

442
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,200
Aku baik-baik saja.

443
00:32:10,780 --> 00:32:13,670
Kamu gimana? Baik juga?

444
00:32:14,210 --> 00:32:16,150
Nggak begitu baik.

445
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:22,000
Dari dulu memang kamu, kan?

446
00:32:26,380 --> 00:32:28,800
Kamu tahu aku suka Hill, kan?

447
00:32:32,420 --> 00:32:33,720
Dari dulu sampai sekarang.

448
00:32:34,490 --> 00:32:35,760
Sejak SMA, lho.

449
00:32:40,570 --> 00:32:43,090
Tapi, dari dulu sampai kini,

450
00:32:43,850 --> 00:32:46,190
Hill nggak pernah mengungkapkan
perasaannya ke siapa pun.

451
00:32:47,060 --> 00:32:48,580
Kecuali ke kamu.

452
00:32:53,320 --> 00:32:55,440
Tapi ada sesuatu yang belum kupahami.

453
00:32:57,710 --> 00:32:59,720
Kenapa kamu meninggalkan Hill?

454
00:33:04,310 --> 00:33:06,520
Aku yang meninggalkan dia?

455
00:33:06,840 --> 00:33:08,810
Itu setelah ospek terakhir, kan?

456
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:11,560
Hill waktu itu sedih banget.

457
00:33:14,250 --> 00:33:16,380
Justru P'Hill yang pergi dari aku.

458
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:21,180
Hill yang meninggalkanmu?

459
00:33:21,350 --> 00:33:22,590
Iya.

460
00:33:23,570 --> 00:33:24,660
Nggak mungkin!

461
00:33:33,530 --> 00:33:36,380
Kamu belum tahu soal Nenek Hill ya?

462
00:33:54,120 --> 00:33:55,220
Hill

463
00:34:01,710 --> 00:34:02,930
Sudah cukup.

464
00:34:10,930 --> 00:34:13,300
Aku sudah tahu soal nenekmu.

465
00:34:17,660 --> 00:34:20,100
Nggak apa-apa, kok.

466
00:34:20,170 --> 00:34:22,360
Semuanya bakal baik-baik saja.

467
00:34:34,460 --> 00:34:35,360
Terima kasih.

468
00:34:41,640 --> 00:34:42,750
Yuk, pergi.

469
00:34:46,240 --> 00:34:47,080
Aku pengen di sini lebih lama.

470
00:34:47,870 --> 00:34:49,840
Kamu sudah mabuk.

471
00:35:09,850 --> 00:35:11,230
Dia sudah pergi.

472
00:35:15,460 --> 00:35:16,980
Dia ninggalin aku.

473
00:35:32,870 --> 00:35:34,960
Apa yang terjadi sama Nenek Hill?
Ada masalah apa?

474
00:35:37,600 --> 00:35:39,120
Nggak ada apa-apa.

475
00:35:42,970 --> 00:35:45,330
Ada sesuatu yang aku nggak ngerti, ya?

476
00:35:47,670 --> 00:35:51,080
Kenapa dia nggak pernah cerita ke aku?

477
00:35:54,440 --> 00:35:57,030
Aku nggak tahu antara kamu sama Hill...

478
00:35:57,140 --> 00:35:58,900
...sebenarnya apa yang terjadi sih?

479
00:36:00,200 --> 00:36:02,500
Tapi apapun alasannya,

480
00:36:03,040 --> 00:36:06,650
sampai seseorang rela simpan sedihnya sendiri.

481
00:36:07,550 --> 00:36:09,270
Kecuali demi...

482
00:36:10,230 --> 00:36:12,380
melindungi orang yang paling dia sayang.

483
00:36:19,670 --> 00:36:21,740
Permisi ya, aku harus pergi.

484
00:36:22,810 --> 00:36:23,940
Sampai ketemu lagi.

485
00:37:04,170 --> 00:37:05,310
Halo.

486
00:37:06,100 --> 00:37:07,530
Kelas kamu sudah selesai belum?

487
00:37:08,770 --> 00:37:09,990
Sudah.

488
00:37:10,210 --> 00:37:13,550
Aku jemput, ya? Hari ini kamu kerja part-time, kan?

489
00:37:14,260 --> 00:37:15,270
Iya.

490
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:19,110
Aku masih kerja di organisasi, tunggu dulu ya.

491
00:37:19,550 --> 00:37:21,980
Oh, aku di sekitar sini, kok.

492
00:37:22,100 --> 00:37:24,760
Nanti hubungi aku lagi aja.

493
00:37:25,090 --> 00:37:26,260
Oke.

494
00:37:36,260 --> 00:37:37,920
Hei, mau ke mana?

495
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:39,490
